Usage: ON [#|+|-|^|&|@]NOTIFY_SIGNOFF_UH [-|^]<parameters> [action]
  This is activated when someone on your notify list (see
  NOTIFY) signs off of irc and both the username and
  the hostname for the person who signed off are known.
  The parameters to the action are:
    $0  Nickname of person who signed off
    $1  Username of person who signed off
    $2  Hostname of person who signed off
